    <summary lang="en_GB">Aegis TV Everywhere — discover-and-auth platform for cable sports</summary>
    <description lang="en_GB">Generic TV-Everywhere client for North American (and eventually UK) cable sports services that authenticate via Adobe Pass SAML — Sportsnet Now (CA), ESPN / Fox Sports / NBC Sports / TNT / CBS Sports (US), and others. Credentials encrypted in the Aegis Vault. Adobe Pass requestor_id and client_version values are discovered at runtime from each provider's own web player so the addon self-heals when those values rotate, eliminating the maintenance burden of legacy hardcoded TVE addons.</description>
